[00:22.756] Yet they always go into raptures at the mere mention of the country. | 然而，他们一提到乡村就欣喜若狂。
[00:27.246] Though they extol the virtues of the peaceful life, | 尽管他们颂扬宁静生活的美德，
[00:30.276] only one of them has ever gone to live in the country, | 但只有一个人曾去乡村居住，
