[00:55.076] the twittering of birds at dawn, | 黎明时鸟儿的啁啾，
[00:57.346] the sight of the rising sun glinting on the trees and pastures. | 以及旭日东升时在树木和牧场上闪耀的景象相比。
[01:02.046] This idyllic pastoral scene is only part of the picture. | 这田园诗般的乡村景象只是一部分。
[01:06.196] My friend fails to mention the long and friendless winter evenings, | 我的朋友没有提到漫长而孤寂的冬夜，
