[01:44.406] If you can do without the few pastoral pleasures of the country, | 如果你能舍弃乡村的那些田园乐趣，
[01:47.676] you will find the city can provide you with the best that life can offer. | 你会发现城市能提供生活中最美好的东西。
[01:52.536] You never have to travel miles to see your friends. | 你从来不需要长途跋涉去看望朋友。
